Internal Energy Parameters
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
use_internal_energy                                          yes
internal_energy_rep_exp                                      12
internal_energy_cutoff                                       100.0
Note: Internal energy only includes repulsive VDW for growth and/or minimization.

